Examples of bids:
Two 1s
Three 3s
One 4

Your bid must always be higher than the last. Neither the face value nor the dice count can go down!

```

~~~ Last Bid ~~~

Keep your response to one sentence. Your response will be directed at your opponents, so be sure not to reveal your dice!
